Experiment 1: Disk Imaging & Hash Verification

Procedure:

Launch FTK Imager / Guymager tool.
Select the source drive (USB/HDD).
Choose “Create Disk Image” option.
Select image format (E01/raw).
Specify destination path for saving image.
Enable hash calculation (SHA-256).
Start imaging process.
After completion, note hash of original and image.
Compare both hash values to verify integrity.
